plot: Frozen, flesh eating Zombies are running amok on a Campus in Ithaca, New York. Meanwhile, Death will stop at nothing to claim its next victim - Claudia.

Ithaca, New York, calls the team's attention when a frosty-breathed, flesh-craving zombie attacks an amorous couple. After capturing it, and immobilizing a second zombie accosting brothers at a frat house, Pete gets bitten, but it's Myka who contracts the zombie-like conditions, leading Artie to reassess their plight. Claudia, meanwhile, bumps into a Warehouse artifact that forewarns her of Death's approach.—statmanjeff
